title: #410 - Troy Conrad
description:
Troy Conrad, Producer of the Set List show (television and live show) and photographer who, among other projects, shoots his "Hall Series," which is black and white photographs of comedians and performers at The Comedy Store in Los Angeles. 

This podcast is brought to you by:
 
Blue Apron: Go to blueapron.com/JOEY to get your first three meals free and free shipping!
 
Texture. Go To texture.com/JOEY to get a free trial for the Texture App. The Texture App gives the use access to hundreds of magazines
 
Recorded live on 09/04/2016.
